FROM (
    SELECT TOP(2) [o].[Id], [o].[DateOfOrder], [o].[InvoiceId], [o].[IsPaid], [o].[Status], [o].[UserId], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[AccessFailedCount], [a].[ConcurrencyStamp], [a].[Email], [a].[EmailConfirmed], [a].[FullName], [a].[LockoutEnabled], [a].[LockoutEnd], [a].[NormalizedEmail], [a].[NormalizedUserName], [a].[PasswordHash], [a].[PhoneNumber], [a].[PhoneNumberConfirmed], [a].[SecurityStamp], [a].[TwoFactorEnabled], [a].[UserName]
    FROM [Orders] AS [o]
    LEFT JOIN [AspNetUsers] AS [a] ON [o].[UserId] = [a].[Id]
    WHERE [o].[Id] = @__id_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [p].[ProductId], [p].[OrderId], [p].[Id], [p].[InvoiceId], [p0].[Id] AS [Id0], [p0].[Category], [p0].[Description], [p0].[Name], [p0].[Price]

    SELECT TOP(2) [o].[Id], [o].[DateOfOrder], [o].[InvoiceId], [o].[IsPaid], [o].[Status], [o].[UserId], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [a].[AccessFailedCount], [a].[ConcurrencyStamp], [a].[Email], [a].[EmailConfirmed], [a].[FullName], [a].[LockoutEnabled], [a].[LockoutEnd], [a].[NormalizedEmail], [a].[NormalizedUserName], [a].[PasswordHash], [a].[PhoneNumber], [a].[PhoneNumberConfirmed], [a].[SecurityStamp], [a].[TwoFactorEnabled], [a].[UserName]
    FROM [Orders] AS [o]
    LEFT JOIN [AspNetUsers] AS [a] ON [o].[UserId] = [a].[Id]
    WHERE [o].[Id] = @__id_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [p].[ProductId], [p].[OrderId], [p].[Id], [p].[InvoiceId], [p0].[Id] AS [Id0], [p0].[Category], [p0].[Description], [p0].[Name], [p0].[Price]
    FROM [ProductOrders] AS [p]
    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p0] ON [p].[ProductId] = [p0].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[OrderId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[ProductId], [t0].[OrderId], [t0].[Id0]"

) AS [t]
